Embattled mayor of the City of Tshwane and DA member, Stevens Mokgalapa, on Sunday announced his intention to resign at the end of this month.In a statement, Mokgalapa says he will resign "before the next Council meeting at the end of February".   Source:   https://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/just-in-embattled-tshwane-mayor-stevens-mokgalapa-announces-resignation-20200202